                            the two cowsheds’. | V: <emph>ol eki t́uźuv́ĺar arasyna</emph>; the same
                            translation as in K. | R: <emph>ol eki t́uźuv́ĺar arasyna</emph>; the
                            same translation as in K.</note>
                        <note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote">An interpretative addition to Gen
                            49:16.</note>
                        <note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote">Lit. ‘sent’.</note>
                    </app>
                </listApp>
